description: Instrumental acoustic versions of all your favourite 1990s hits! These piano and acoustic guitar-based instrumental versions are perfect for playing in the background while you work, rest or play, and are also ideal for coffee shops, cafes, hotel lobbies, restaurants, lifts and hold music/muzak!
